[l] Die ACLU hat sich mal Whistleblower-Kanaele angeschaut, also die Methoden, ueber die man als Whistleblower so offiziell auf Missstaende hinweisen kann. Und wenig ueberraschend war das eine Katastrophe.We identified dozens of inspectors general, including those at the Departments of Justice and Homeland Security, who do not use encryption to protect online whistleblower complaints of waste, fraud, and abuse. The State Department’s “Rewards for Justice” online terrorism tip line also does not use encryption.OMFGLOLWUT
